tafsir[4]{c,v,t}:
  15,93,"We will question them about the disbelief and sins they committed in the world."
  15,96,"Those who take another deity along with Allah. They will soon come to know the evil outcome of their associating partners with Allah."
  15,99,"Go on worshipping your Lord and continue doing so as long as you live until death comes to you in that state."
  16,6,"There is beauty in them for you in the evening and in the morning when you take them out to graze."